# Mobile E2E MCP（中文版）

[![CI（build + typecheck + unit + smoke）](https://github.com/shenyuexin/mobile-e2e-mcp/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg?branch=main)](https://github.com/shenyuexin/mobile-e2e-mcp/actions/workflows/ci.yml)
